avertise() in NodeHandle class <--> Methods that connects to the master to publicize that the node will be publishing messages on the given topic and it returns a publisher

<arg> tag in roslaunch file <--> tag in roslaunch file for specifying values to pass through the command line

substitution args <--> roslaunch arguments sets with the sintax $() resolved prior to node launch in a launch file  

genmsg <--> Standalone Python library for generating ROS message and service data structures for various languages.

piaram vs rosparam <--> The first are tags for setting a single parameterm the second are used for setting groups or more complex structures of parameters.  

urdf (ROS package) <--> parser for the Unified Robot Description Format

lookupTransorm(frame2,frame1) in transform_listener.h  <--> It returns the transformation to frame2 from frame1 and the methods are in order frame2, frame1 
